    <section class="container">
        <div class="LTdesc" style="margin-top: 7rem; margin-bottom: 7rem;">
            <p>
                <b style="font-style: italic;">LapakTani</b> is a web-based agricultural e-commerce. This platform is dedicated to our local farmers, helping them to promote and sell their crops and other farm products with ease.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="line"></div>

