                <h1><b>Vision</b></h1>
            </div>
            <div class="visionDesc">
                <p>We aim to be the biggest agricultural e-commerce in Indonesia, help local farmers to be more prosperous, and deliver fresh and locally sourced products</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="line"></div>

        <div class="mission d-flex justify-content-center">
            <div class="missionDesc">
                <p>Creating a handy platform for local farmers to conveniently and efficiently advertise and sell their crops, without any middlemen intervention.</p>
            </div>
